      <title>麦当劳系统中断影响全球门店</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/mcdonald-s-system-outage-affects-stores-across-asia-and-australia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[麦当劳公司受到系统中断的打击，该系统中断似乎始于亚太地区并蔓延到全球其他市场，导致顾客无法在其商店和通过电子平台订购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/mcdonald-s-system-outage-affects-stores-across-asia-and-australia</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 07:55:56 GMT</pubDate>
